text: Chuyunchi () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Chuyunchinsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 475 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Chuyunchi
